ءَهُمْ ۚ وَمَنْ أَضَلُّ مِمَّنِ ٱتَّبَعَ هَوَىٰهُ بِغَيْرِ هُدًۭى مِّنَ ٱللَّهِ ۚ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ لَا يَهْدِى ٱلْقَوْمَ ٱلظَّٰلِمِينَ","translation":"And since they cannot respond to this thy challenge, know that they are following only their own likes and dislikes: and who could be more astray than he who follows [but] his own likes and dislikes without any guidance from God? Verily, God does not grace with His guidance peo­ple who are given to evildoing!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3302.mp3","surahId":28,"words":[{"id":48834,"position":1,"arabic":"فَإِن","translation":"অতঃপর যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/028_050_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48835,"position":2,"arabic":"لَّمْ","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/028_050_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48836,"position":3,"arabic":"يَسْتَجِيبُوا۟","translation":"তারা সাড়া দেয়","audioUrl":"wbw/028_050_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48837,"position":4,"arabic":"لَكَ","translation":"প্রতি তোমার (ডাকে)","audioUrl":"wbw/028_050_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48838,"position":5,"arabic":"فَٱعْلَمْ","translation":"তবে জেনে রাখো","audioUrl":"wbw/028_050_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48839,"position":6,"arabic":"أَنَّمَا","translation":"কেবল","audioUrl":"wbw/028_050_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48840,"position":7,"arabic":"يَتَّبِعُونَ","translation":"তারা অনুসরণ করছে","audioUrl":"wbw/028_050_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48841,"position":8,"arabic":"أَهْوَآءَهُمْ ۚ","translation":"খেয়ালখুশিগুলোর তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/028_050_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48843,"position":9,"arabic":"وَمَنْ","translation":"আর কে (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/028_050_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48844,"position":10,"arabic":"أَضَلُّ","translation":"অধিক বিভ্রান্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/028_050_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":48845,"position":11,"arabic":"مِمَّنِ","translation":"(তার) চেয়ে যে","audioUrl":"wbw/028_050_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"